  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 874b5e5991c8ddd4c9ddbc996be428fb, type: 3}
  m_Name: IntroMail
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Mail
  sender: stillwoodparks@yurimail.com
  subject: Your New Assignment
  body: "Ivan Navorsky, \r\nWe regret to inform you that a series of\u2026 unfortunate
    events have necessitated me and my associates to oversee the complete evacuation
    of your park. We have managed to secure all  entrances to the park except the
    one on the northeastern exit used for emergency fire escapes.\r\nWe spoke with
    your supervisor and have been informed that you have control to remotely open
    and close the gate.\r\nLost guests will be approaching the northeastern gate
    exit and buzzing you over the intercom to request exit as part of the ongoing
    evacuation, and due to the storm. However, we\u2019ve received some reports of
    some\u2026 \u2018unsavory individuals\u2019 trying to impersonate park guests.
    These should NOT be allowed to exit under any circumstance.\r\nWe have managed
    to retrieve detailed descriptions of all guests and personnel still remaining
    in your section of the park that can be found on your computer. How we retrieved
    this information is none of your concern.\r\nWhen a guest buzzes in at the gate
    ask them questions and compare their answers AND PERSONALITY to the directory.
    If a guest has information that does not match what\u2019s in the directory,
    or their personality does not match the one in the directory, do not open the
    gate for them, and ask them to leave. A liquidation team will be sent to deal
    with them as soon as we have the staff free.\r\nLastly some of these\u2026entities,
    have been found to cause irregularities in radio waves. If you notice any static,
    pitch changing, or other regularities in your radio while talking to a guest.
    Do not forget to check the radio for every guest and if it\u2019s irregular DO
    NOT ALLOW THEM TO EXIT UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCE. \r\nWe are expecting your utmost
    discretion in this matter. Failure will not be tolerated.\n\r\n-M.S.\r\n"
